| Password reset flow | ❌ Not implemented |
| Pagination | ❌ All items loaded at once |
| API/JSON endpoints | ❌ HTML-only rendering |
| Config management | ❌ No config.py or env-based config |
| Docker | ❌ No containerization |
| Flask app factory pattern | ❌ Single-file monolith (526 lines) |

